Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是赤報隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一隊隊長相樂對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我乃是官軍參謀進藤帶刀\N前來傳達總督府的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.17,0:01:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今你們的任務已結束\N辛苦啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事過十年\N終於又是赤報隊登場的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十三話\N左之助的背叛！？命運之再會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錦繪…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我手邊的工作都放不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，要我替你去買是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，可不可以拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.92,0:02:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂、喂，你別人不找\N想叫左之助先生打你啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，不怕死的小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.73,0:02:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊！打他的事交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說真的啊，左之先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有關係\N老是讓他請客….對吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.84,0:02:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是請\N全部都是讓你欠著而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼不知道…\N不過我可沒錢還你….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.31,0:03:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒有期待你現在就還\N所以我有幫你算利息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備慢慢地等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利、利息？牛肉火鍋的錢\N有人算利息的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起！你真是商人的榜樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去….算了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，是要買誰的，哪種畫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡津南畫的劍客\N伊庭八郎喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕府末期最受歡迎的劍士\N「赤靴之伊庭八」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還看不出來\N有這種輕浮的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我就去走一遭吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，對不起….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.25,0:03:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.88,0:03:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有話就說，直載了當地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雀兒….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.29,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事，真的沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.06,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N那麼買月岡津的伊庭八二張吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.87,0:03:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是左之先生，高人一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊\N如果再加上都能按照付錢給我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.04,0:04:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然變得隨和的左之先生是不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過以前的左之先生也很迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，打架騅「斬左」！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來，臉上帶著笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心裏卻一點也不滿足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.02,0:04:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如同將爆發的炸彈般\N總是閃閃耀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.00,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，是兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買錦繪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.87,0:04:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次聽說左之助\N也有這種興趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是美人圖吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是春畫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭春畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上信以為真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妙紅著臉拜託我的\N可不是買我自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.93,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆，月岡津南的伊庭八我要兩張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,津南的伊庭八是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人，你運氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏，正好是最後的兩張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,津南的畫很受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一下子就賣光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是屬於美帥型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二張一共十錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我沒帶錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐先借一點給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是，一定要還喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西叫作錦繪\N倒是各式各樣都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.66,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是，相樂隊長….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣是津南的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只那張賣不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.37,0:05:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而他卻都一定畫他\N那位冒牌官軍頭目的畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡，住哪裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,津南那傢伙，人在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真，真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老先生你多說了廢話….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他住隔壁村的簡陋大雜房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.39,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，那人討厭和人來往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去了，他也不會見你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小子不可能不見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，好熏啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到裏面去等吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿松，你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小富也買了秋刀魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡先生….不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡先生你在吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原赤報隊預備隊員月岡克浩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畫是你畫的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你….怎麼會….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.00,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一看就知道了\N隊長的身邊有以前的你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畫，別人是畫不出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，沒想到你還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.05,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比此比此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛…畫師\N月岡津南也是赤報隊殘留隊員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家吧！薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，劍心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，赤報隊對左之而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有特殊的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在回憶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,局外人是不需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，沒想到你成個畫畫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，從前你就很靈巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用大炮，調火藥等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼難的事都能簡單地做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經十年了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.36,0:07:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，相樂隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我準備食物來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，大豐收！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙還不快死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓魚逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，這小子掉了三隻鯉魚啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說好不說的嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜，什麼事都要報告隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不守信用，王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突擊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是幕府的兵，快起來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助，克浩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.97,0:08:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們到安全的地方去避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死也不會離開隊長身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也是赤報隊的一份子呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事！擦傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很危險的，你這王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼，危險的是你啊傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了， 王八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋和傻瓜卻都還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，你目前在作什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊，只是個流浪漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，順其自然挺快樂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛，你過得挺快樂的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這十年從沒快樂過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才遇到你以前從來沒笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給相樂隊長和我們赤報隊\N戴上污名的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恨著他們渡過了這十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前也和你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.55,0:09:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天，所有都準備\N萬全之時能和你相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為是隊長的指引….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克你….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助，我和你\N再次重組赤報隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒陷害我們\N赤報隊的維新政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現相樂隊長理想之新時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是說要打倒政府….你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的計劃毫無缺點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看！我利用在赤報隊學的\N檢藥知識所製成的炸藥彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克，你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.82,0:10:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的十年！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟然如此地….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個\N首先是內務省  然後….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來把各省廳給炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要反政府火花在東京發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在全國各地不平的士族和\N農民們一定會一齊響應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，就等著看\N明治政府崩壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有用的….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之  難道你不憎恨\N污賴我們赤報隊的明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想把它打垮嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.39,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋東西！我當然恨明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，我知道\N那不是我所辦得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.73,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和持續了三百年的\N德川幕府比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.76,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明治政府也不過才十幾年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑我就能把它炸的粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使你爆破成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.84,0:11:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全國也未必會一擁而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克，你要知道\N推翻明治政府是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.31,0:11:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，對你而言赤報隊\N似乎已是過去之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在活得快活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒打算再拖你下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊克….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.76,0:11:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個王八左之已不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.89,0:11:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年來，天天想著為赤報隊\N和隊長洗清罪名的他而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是看不清現實的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已十年了….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他媽的，吹起冷風來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你，你們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強，強盜啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了建設新的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們赤報隊要徵收你的寶物\N作為軍用資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤….赤報隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雀真會拍球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這幾天，已有七間被搶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用炸裂彈，手法還真粗暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.96,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是舊赤報隊員所為嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面寫著每次都有留下\N相樂隊長的錦繪….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是左之助做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑，不可以亂說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.57,0:12:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然左之助曾擅自到人家裏吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借了錢不還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會白吃白喝，然後….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈不是沒做一件好事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈！人的優點不是\N用嘴巴可以說得清的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.09,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交往過後才知道能不能信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助即使不小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不會做那種強盜做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事，我也知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.80,0:13:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，他一直都以\N相樂隊長之事自吹自擂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是，為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長的錦繪會….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個人會不會有關連
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畫師？你是說月岡津南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望不是最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，能遇到你，我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克….不要是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.77,0:13:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克跑到那兒去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀次兄怎麼了，臉色都變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的，聽到個奇怪傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想應該和\N左之先生有關係….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼傳言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說，在西町的賭場\N有個傢伙最近很闊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽那傢伙說這都是\N托赤報隊的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像叫什麼紅鼻子的新藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅鼻子的新藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N讓你們為了我到處奔波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect, 下次送禮謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了，說什麼送禮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.45,0:14:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我倆是因為迷上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你和以前的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.19,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長的畫？案件的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的   不要錢都賣不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想問什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案件發生之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有哪家店整批地\N賣了相樂隊長的畫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，最近我們同行都在說\N對面鎮上畫店賣了一批
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果問那店裏的人就\N大概可以知道是誰買的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.57,0:15:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這麼一說，倒想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才，津南也來問同樣問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡津南嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點二點是丁啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了今天真倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近新藏先生景氣不錯嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說你找到了搖錢樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是真的嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，托赤報隊財神爺的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅鼻子的新藏先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰，你是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是誰，你別管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.12,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前不是叫什麼\N不知火黨的強盜團的手下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要回答我的問題即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰，誰要回答你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想回答，我也要你說說\N你最喜歡的赤報隊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真慢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很報歉！那小子又去\N賭場了吧.去叫來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天要搶的對象是….！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.69,0:16:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,油類的大盤，清水屋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是清水屋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以收集美術品出名的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.53,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們拿得到的份\N這次似乎會很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩，日本的美術品\N很受橫濱外國人貿易商喜愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以賣很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼….警察方面呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.14,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以為是舊赤報隊干的\N正拚命地在找尋殘黨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.65,0:17:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越想越覺得赤報隊的人\N真是可悲啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是維新志士，又是警察幹部\N進藤先生，我們也能夠安泰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來進藤先生\N才算是真正的壞人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.86,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想一生\N在警察局當公務員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.63,0:17:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時代錢最好用\N我還需要更多的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.57,0:17:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只好讓赤報隊\N繼續當壞人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新藏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.24,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到，你竟成了\N不知火黨的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用赤報隊的名義搶錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.85,0:17:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原官軍參謀，進藤帶刀先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這位陷害相樂隊長\N和我們赤報隊的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子，你到底是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原赤報隊予備隊員\N相樂左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！相樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原赤報隊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你靠捉到相樂隊長的功勞\N升為警察幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻利用赤報隊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.04,0:17:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底作弄我們赤報隊幾次\N你才甘心，絕對不饒你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用客氣，把他給我殺了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就你這二招還想….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！到外面去好好跟你們玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作還真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜生，眼睛閉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在，殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.36,0:18:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追查收購相樂隊長畫的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.26,0:18:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於被我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些冒牌的赤報隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克，讓他們好好的看看\N真正的赤報隊打架的樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畜生！你根本不是對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,料理好了，左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些雜魚都料理好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的就是你了進藤帶刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你們原赤報隊員的屍體\N放在犯罪現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.98,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好作為是原赤報隊\N做的最佳證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.38,0:19:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們特地前來，謝啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳傢伙….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧！啊克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心，擦傷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過了十年，你還是個傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，而你也還是個王八蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這裏，這間房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞到後院去，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.00,0:20:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為聽說搶倉庫\N是使用炸裂彈…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，以為是我幹的，是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.47,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.54,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為我會生氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.44,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，幹嘛道歉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.84,0:20:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，記住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.28,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打倒的是明治政府\N象進藤那種利用我們赤報隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用相樂隊長橫行霸道的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.99,0:21:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，建立真正\N四民平等的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.83,0:21:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此而已，再見了，傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下！王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種王八蛋\N我可不會讓你一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動之日決定了，通知我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.08,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之你這囂張的傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的朋友雖然重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.88,0:21:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是和以前的朋友比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不捨棄現在的所有……

